Pre-Game Insights: Oman could emerge as the dark horses of the groups who could end up giving a tough fight to the well-established opponents.
Miscellaneous Highlights: Oman will begin its 2024T20 World Cup journey by taking on African side Namibia
Oman is pooled in Group B alongside defending champions England as well as former winners Australia.
Namibia and Scotland are the other members of the group.
Others: Oman T20 World Cup 2024 squad: Aqib Ilyas (Captain), Zeeshan Maqsood, Kashyap Prajapati, Pratik Athavale, Ayaan Khan, Shoaib Khan, Mohammad Nadeem, Naseem Khushi, Mehran Khan, Bilal Khan, Rafiullah, Kaleemullah, Fayyaz Butt, Shakeel Ahmad, Khalid Kail. Reserves: Jatinder Singh, Samay Shrivastava, Sufyan Mehmood, Jay Odedra
